reviewText: I would have given it a 5 star if not that the referenced document download for use in the course was not available. I looked everywhere, others had same feedback.
Various technical problems - attachments not visible/Cloud workspace failed etc.

Overall great course but missing PDF materials made it frustrating but not impossible to finish. Would have saved some time if instructions on what to prep before starting were provided, like where to get the additional materils or that you will need log in details for the program you are using.
T​his was really great thank you for this course
Quite basic course but contains all necessary information and frameworks to get acquainted with the Trello tool. Instructor was good
